NK083('u)002:365: rgyun gtor gsum bdun bcu gcig la sogs btang //
NK083('u)002:366: rnam dag bdun dang phyi nang gsang mchod 'bul //
NK083('u)002:367: de rnams gsang sngags lam gyi sngon 'gro yin //
NK083('u)002:368: bslab pa gsum la lam gzhi bca' ba ni //
NK083('u)002:369: mi mthun slong sems mnyam 'jog rang ngo shes //
NK083('u)002:370: sh+ai la sa m+aa ti pradz+ny+aa shik+sha na //
NK083('u)002:371: gnod sbyor log zhugs khyad par thabs kyis zin //
NK083('u)002:372: bden pa'i don mthong goms 'dris de mi 'da' //gnyen po'i dbang gis brgyad khri bzhi stong gsungs //
NK083('u)002:373: sems gsum sgo nas lam la 'jug pa ni //
NK083('u)002:374: yid 'ong pha mar shes shing bde ldan bsgom //
NK083('u)002:375: sems can pha ma sdug bsngal bral bar bsam //
NK083('u)002:376: sangs rgyas thob 'dod bsam pa len dang sgrub //
NK083('u)002:377: sems gsum sde gsum bslab gsum nyams gsum thugs //
NK083('u)002:378: khyad par gsang sngags lam gyi ngo bo ni //
NK083('u)002:379: bum gsang ye shes bde chen dbang bzhi bskur //
NK083('u)002:380: phyi nang snod bcud gzhal yas lha ru bskyed //
NK083('u)002:381: skye 'gags gnyis med rang byung mtha' las 'das //
NK083('u)002:382: gnad gsum gcun pas rtog med rang gsal 'char //
NK083('u)002:383: so spyi bogs gsang yang dag kho nar spyod //
NK083('u)002:384: mnyam rjes bza' bcang bsrung ba'i dam lnga dbog /de rnams gsang sngags lam gyi ngo bo yin //
NK083('u)002:385: rnal 'byor lnga yis nyams su blangs pa ni //
NK083('u)002:386: rtog med chos skur nyal la 'chi rtog sbyang //
NK083('u)002:387: 'gag med longs skur langs te skye rtog sbyang //
NK083('u)002:388: dbang bzhis bdud rtsir brlabs la bza' btung rol //
NK083('u)002:389: sna tshogs thabs kyis bzung la lam du btang //
NK083('u)002:390: drod srod skyes shar 'da' ka bar do bltem //
NK083('u)002:391: lam de'i gegs bzhi'i skyon bsal bstan pa ni //
NK083('u)002:392: bying rgod nyams gsum bcos la lam du btang //
NK083('u)002:393: nad kyi gzhi rgyu rkyen 'bras ngos bzung bcos //
NK083('u)002:394: spros bral ngang bzhag rgyun chad skyi dang sel //
NK083('u)002:395: gnod pa'i zas bza' 'phrig bcad ltos med bsgyur //
NK083('u)002:396: dkar dmar nag po'i h'u 'phros steng 'og gdon //
NK083('u)002:397: rang las gzhan med yang 'khu 'phrig bcad //
NK083('u)002:398: dam nyams grogs gnas zas kyi grib bzhi bsal //
NK083('u)002:399: lam de'i bogs 'don gnad du btang ba ni //
NK083('u)002:400: skyon gyi rtsa ba bdag 'dzin blo yis btang //
NK083('u)002:401: yon tan gzhi ma nyams len drag po bya //
NK083('u)002:402: rang gi lam la bogs med gzhan gyis 'don //
NK083('u)002:403: nyon mongs gnad nas gzung la lam du btang //
NK083('u)002:404: rnam rtog lam du btang la bogs su 'don //
NK083('u)002:405: de rnams lam gyi cha rkyen yan lag yin //
NK083('u)002:406: lam de mthar phyin mngon gyur 'bras bu ni //
NK083('u)002:407: sku lnga gsung lnga thugs yon phrin las lnga //
NK083('u)002:408: rten can rten med ngo bo nyid don byed //
NK083('u)002:409: gcig dang tha dad gnyis su med par bzhugs //
NK083('u)002:410: gzigs tshul grub dang ma grub bden brdzun brtag /tshe 'dir sangs rgyas thob byed nye ba'i lam //
NK083('u)002:411: rang mtshan mngon du ston pa nges pa'i chos //
NK083('u)002:412: thabs dang shes rab gnyis ldan shing rta'i srol //
NK083('u)002:413: pham byed rgyal 'gyur bla med theg mchog go //
NK083('u)002:414: 'di sbyar dge ba dri med rnam dag gis //
NK083('u)002:415: lus can thams cad smin grol lam zhugs te //
NK083('u)002:416: rang chas shes rtogs sgrib dag nyes zad nas //
NK083('u)002:417: yang dag rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas myur thob shog /gsang
NK083('u)002:418: sngags lam gyi rim pa rin po che gsal ba'i
NK083('u)002:420: o rgyan gyi slob dpon chen po pad+ma sam b+ha was mdzad pa rdzogs so //
NK083('u)002:421: rig 'dzin rje'i phyag bris dpe ltar zhus so //
NK083('u)002:422: nang bshad gsang sngags lam rim sa bcad bzhugs so //
NK083('u)002:423: dpal kun tu bzang po la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK083('u)002:424: nang bshad gsang sngags lam gyi rim pa 'di la don gsum ste /
NK083('u)002:429: gnyis bcom gnyis ldan phyag 'tshal ba dang /
NK083('u)002:430: bdag nyid rnal 'byor rtsom par dam bca' ba'o //
NK083('u)002:435: gzhung gi spyi don dang po gzhi la gnyis te /
NK083('u)002:437: gnyis med lhun grub gnas lugs dang /
NK083('u)002:438: snying po ma rig 'khrul lugs so //
NK083('u)002:439: gzhung gi spyi don gnyis pa lam la gsum ste /
NK083('u)002:440: lam gyi sngon du 'gro ba dang /
NK083('u)002:441: lam rang gi ngo bo dang /
NK083('u)002:442: lam gyi cha rkyen bstan pa'o //
NK083('u)002:444: phun sum tshogs pa lngas sgrub pa'i gzhi bzung ba dang /
NK083('u)002:445: bsrung ba'i 'khor lo'i rim pa bstan pa dang /
NK083('u)002:446: gnad lnga'i sgo nas lam la 'jug par bstan pa'o //
NK083('u)002:448: phun sum tshogs pa lngas gnas gang du dang /
NK083('u)002:449: dad gus dbang dam gang zag gang gis dang /
NK083('u)002:450: tshes skar gza' bzang dus gang la dang /
NK083('u)002:451: zas sman mchod skong rdzas gang bsags pa dang /
NK083('u)002:452: ma dred rtse gcig thabs ji ltar bsgrub pa'o //
NK083('u)002:453: gnyis pa bsrung 'khor la drug ste /
NK083('u)002:454: rnal 'byor srung ba'i byang chub sems kyi srung ba dang /
NK083('u)002:455: lha mtshan rdo rje mtshon cha lnga'i srung ba dang /
NK083('u)002:456: lus ngag sems gsum yi ge gsum gyi srung ba dang /
NK083('u)002:457: spyan ras 'jam dpal zhi drag gsum brtsegs kyis srung ba dang /
NK083('u)002:458: rdo rje ra bas rang byung lhun gyis grub pa'i srung ba dang /
NK083('u)002:459: bya byad ngo bo don dam mtshan ma med pa'i srung ba'o //
NK083('u)002:460: gsum pa gan da lngas theg chen lam du 'jug pa la lnga ste /
NK083('u)002:461: gnad lnga'i sgo nas skyabs 'gros chos kyi gzhi gting ba dang /
NK083('u)002:462: dkar dmar nag gsum yig brgyas sgrib pa sbyang ba dang /
NK083('u)002:463: dpal 'byor las 'bras las 'bras mi rtag pa sgom pa la blo sbyangs pa dang /
NK083('u)002:464: sgrub dang mchod pa'i man+dala dang /
NK083('u)002:465: sna tshogs lam khyer gtor ma btang bas tshogs bsags pa dang /
NK083('u)002:467: mchod pa phul la tshogs gnyis yongs su spel ba'o //
NK083('u)002:468: gnyis pa lam rang gi ngo bo la gnyis te /
NK083('u)002:469: thun mong spyi yi lam dang /
NK083('u)002:470: khyad par gsang sngags kyi lam mo //
NK083('u)002:472: bslab pa gsum la lam gyi gzhi bca' ba dang /
NK083('u)002:473: sems gsum gyis lam gyi kha bsgyur ba'o //
NK083('u)002:476: ngo bo ngos bzung ba dang /
NK083('u)002:477: sh+ai la sa m+aa mtshon bya'i sgra don bshad pa dang /
NK083('u)002:478: gnod sbyin log zhugs mtshon byed kyi rang ldog bstan pa dang /
NK083('u)002:479: bden pa'i don mthong mtshan gzhi skye tshul dang /
NK083('u)002:480: gnyen po'i dbang gis gnyen po'i sgo nas rnam grangs su 'gyur tshul lo //
NK083('u)002:481: gnyis pa sems gsum gyis lam gyi kha bsgyur ba la bzhi ste /
NK083('u)002:482: sems gsum sgo nas byams pa dang /
NK083('u)002:483: sems can pha ma snying rje dang /
NK083('u)002:484: sangs rgyas thob 'dod byang chub kyi sems dang /
NK083('u)002:485: sems gsum sde gsum de dag sde snod gsum du ngos bzung la bslab pa gsum du bstan pa'o //
NK083('u)002:486: gnyis pa gsang sngags rang gi lam la lnga ste /
NK083('u)002:487: khyad par gsang sngags rgyud smin par byed pa dbang dang /
NK083('u)002:489: smin pa grol bar byed pa la lta ba dang /
NK083('u)002:490: gnad gsum gcun pas lta ba goms par byed pa la bsgom pa dang /
NK083('u)002:491: so spyi'i bogs gsang de dang mi 'bral shing rtsal sbyong ba la spyod pa dang /
NK083('u)002:492: mnyam rjes bza' bca' de dag las mi 'da' bar byed pa la dam tshig go //
NK083('u)002:493: gnyis pa lta ba la gnyis te /
NK083('u)002:494: phyi nang snod bcud bskyed rim sbyang pa dang /
NK083('u)002:495: skye 'gags gnyis med rdzogs rim bstan pa'o //
NK083('u)002:496: gsum pa de'i cha rkyen bstan pa la gsum ste /
NK083('u)002:497: rnal 'byor lnga'i lam nyams len gyi gnad bstan pa dang /
NK083('u)002:498: gegs sel bzhis lam gyi rkyen bsal ba dang /
NK083('u)002:501: rnal 'byor lngas rtog med chos skur nyal ba'i rnal 'byor dang /
NK083('u)002:502: 'gag med longs skur ldang ba'i rnal 'byor dang /
NK083('u)002:503: dbang bzhis bdud rtsir za ba'i rnal 'byor dang /
NK083('u)002:504: sna tshogs thabs kyis rgyun gyi rnal 'byor dang /
NK083('u)002:505: drod brod skyes shar dus gnad kyi rnal 'byor ro //
NK083('u)002:506: gnyis pa lam gyi gegs bsal ba la bzhi ste /
NK083('u)002:507: lam de'i gegs bzhi bying rgod nyams gsum ting nge 'dzin nyams kyi gegs bsal ba dang /
NK083('u)002:508: nad kyi gzhi rgyu lus na tsha sdug bsngal gyi gegs bsal ba dang /
NK083('u)002:509: rang las gzhan med sems rnam rtog lha 'dre'i gegs bsal ba dang /
NK083('u)002:510: dam nyams grogs gnas rkyen snang glo bur grib kyi gegs bsal ba'o //
NK083('u)002:511: gsum pa lam gyi bogs 'don pa la gsum ste /
NK083('u)002:513: skyon gyi rtsa ba bogs mi 'byung ba'i skyon bsal ba dang /
NK083('u)002:514: yon tan gzhi ma 'byung ba'i gzhi bca' ba dang /
NK083('u)002:515: bogs ji ltar 'don pa'i thabs so //
NK083('u)002:517: rang gi lam la rang lam la gnas pa de la bogs 'don pa dang /
NK083('u)002:518: sngar med gsar du skyes pa'i nyon mongs pa rnam rtog bogs su 'don pa'o //
NK083('u)002:520: nyon mongs gnad kyis nyon mongs bogs su 'don pa dang /
NK083('u)002:521: rnam rtog lam du rnam rtog bogs su 'don pa'o //
NK083('u)002:522: gzhung gi spyi don gsum pa /
NK083('u)002:523: lam nyams su blang nas mthar phyin pa'i 'bras bu la bzhi ste /
NK083('u)002:525: sku lnga gsum lnga 'bras chos ngos bzung ba dang /
NK083('u)002:528: gcig dang tha dad dgongs pa la bzhugs lugs dang /
NK083('u)002:529: gzigs tshul grub dang gdul bya la thugs rjes 'dzin tshul la gzhan gyi log rtog dgag pa'o //
NK083('u)002:530: spyi don gsum pa mjug gi don la gsum ste /
NK083('u)002:531: tshe 'dir sangs rgyas chos kyi che ba bstan pa dang /
NK083('u)002:532: 'di sbyar dge ba dge ba thams cad mkhyen par bsngo zhing /
NK083('u)002:533: gsang sngags lam gyi rim mtshan rdzogs tshul dang bcas pa bstan pa'o //
NK083('u)002:534: nang bshad gsang sngags lam rim gyi bsdus don rdzogs so //
NK083('u)002:535: gsang sngags lam rim gyi snying po sems nyid gcer ston lag khrid lnga pa bzhugs so //
NK083('u)002:536: bla ma dam pa rnams la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK083('u)002:537: gu ru pad+ma 'byung gnas kyi mdzad pa'i man ngag
NK083('u)002:538: /sems nyid gcer ston gyi lag khrid 'di la lnga
NK083('u)002:539: ste / dang po rang sems lta ru gzhug pa /
NK083('u)002:540: gnyis pa ma mthong na sems ngo bstan pa /
NK083('u)002:541: gsum pa mthong ba'i don ngo sprod pa /
NK083('u)002:542: bzhi pa de'i rgyab skyor ba /
NK083('u)002:545: rang gi sems gang yin ltos la /
NK083('u)002:546: lan cig khyer la shog /byas pas /
NK083('u)002:547: sems stong pa nyid lta rgyu med pa gcig 'dug /zer na /
NK083('u)002:549: snang ba thams cad sems su 'dug /zer na'ang /
NK083('u)002:550: sems kyi spyi rig tsam mthong ba yin gyis /
NK083('u)002:551: da lta ba'i rang sems ngos ma zin pa yin /
NK083('u)002:552: nam mkha' dang sa gzhi ri bo la sogs pa gang nas btsal yang mi rnyed do //
NK083('u)002:553: gnyis pa sems ngo bstan pa ni /
NK083('u)002:554: sems kyi spyi rig tsam gyis mthong ba'i go mi chod do //
NK083('u)002:555: da lta gang shar de ngos zin dgos pa yin /
NK083('u)002:556: da thabs sgra de sems su shar ba yin te /
NK083('u)002:557: ngas sems gang yin ltos shig byas pa khyod kyi sems su shar ba yin te /
NK083('u)002:558: khyod rang gang yin lta ba po de rang sems yin no //
NK083('u)002:560: ma dang bu'i dpes ngo sprad do //
NK083('u)002:561: de yang sems la ltos shig ces pa'i /
NK083('u)002:562: sgra des sems la tshur bltas sam /
NK083('u)002:563: sems kyis sgra phar bzung ngam /
NK083('u)002:564: sgra sems dbyer med du 'dug ltos shig /byas la dri /
NK083('u)002:565: snga ma gnyis po ltar zer na /
NK083('u)002:568: go ba yin pas ngo sprad par bya'o //
NK083('u)002:569: de bzhin du gzugs la sogs pa yul lnga ka sems su ngo sprad do //
NK083('u)002:570: gsum pa mthong ba'i don ngo sprod pa la gsum ste /
NK083('u)002:573: ngo bo ga nyis med du ngo sprad pa'o //
NK083('u)002:575: gang yin ltab po'i sems de rang du 'dug gam /
NK083('u)002:580: ngo mthong ba yin pas ngo sprad do //
NK083('u)002:581: gzhan ma yin par thag bcad la /
NK083('u)002:582: rang snang la gzhug pas rang grol du shes 'gro ba yin no //
NK083('u)002:583: rang du shes pas gzhan 'dzin gyi rtog pa mi skye ba ni /
NK083('u)002:584: rang grol gyi gnad yin no //
NK083('u)002:586: ye grol ngo sprad pa ni /
NK083('u)002:587: lta ba ltar snang ba'i sems de snang ba rang rgyud du bden pa gcig 'dug gam /
NK083('u)002:592: tshur bkug nas stong par 'dug gam /
NK083('u)002:593: yal ba'i rjes la stong par 'dug gam /
NK083('u)002:594: de ka rang stong par 'dug dri /
NK083('u)002:595: snga ma gnyis po ltar zer na /
NK083('u)002:597: de ka rang stong par 'dug zer na /
NK083('u)002:598: ngo bo mthong ba yin pas ngo sprad do //
NK083('u)002:599: snang ba rang rgyud pa bden pa min par thag
NK083('u)002:600: bcad la stong pa nyid la gzhug pas ye grol
NK083('u)002:602: stong par shes pas snang ba la bden 'dzin mi skye /
NK083('u)002:603: de ka ye grol gyi gnad yin no //
NK083('u)002:605: gnyis med ngo sprad pa ni /
NK083('u)002:606: stong pa cang med cig 'dug gam /
NK083('u)002:607: gsal rig dang bcas pa cig 'dug gam dri /
NK083('u)002:611: gsal ba dang stong pa tha dad du 'dug gam /
NK083('u)002:616: ngo bo mthong ba yin pas ngo sprad do //
NK083('u)002:617: snang stong tha dad du med par gnyis med la
NK083('u)002:618: gzhug pas gnyis med du ngo shes 'gro ba yin
NK083('u)002:619: no // gnyis med la gnas pas gnyis 'dzin gyi rtog pa mi skye /
NK083('u)002:620: de ka la gnyis med rtogs zer ba yin no //
NK083('u)002:621: bzhi pa rgyab skyor la gsum ste /
NK083('u)002:622: rang grol gyi rgyab skyor ba /
NK083('u)002:623: rnam pa'i chos thams cad kyi gshis la ye yin ye grol las med de /
NK083('u)002:625: mi gar phyin sa steng las mi 'da' ba bzhin du dang /
NK083('u)002:626: ye grol gyi rgyab skyor ba /
NK083('u)002:627: chos thams cad kyi gshis la ye yin ye grol las 'da' sa med de /
NK083('u)002:629: chu gling na chu las 'da' sa med pa lta bu dang /
NK083('u)002:630: gnyis med kyi rgyab skyor ba la /
NK083('u)002:631: chos thams cad kyi ngo bo la gnyis med las 'da' sa med de /
NK083('u)002:633: me la tsha ba las 'da' sa med pa lta bu'o //
NK083('u)002:634: lta ba'i skabs su shes par bya'o //
NK083('u)002:636: la bzla ba la gsum ste /
NK083('u)002:638: kun gyi bdag nyid du la bzla ba'o //
NK083('u)002:640: sems kyi rtsal snang 'gag med du shar ba la gzhan gyi rtog pa ka nas dag pa ni /
NK083('u)002:641: ye shes ka dag /shar tshad kyi rang bzhin stong
NK083('u)002:642: pa la dngos po rang brgyud kyis bden pa ka
NK083('u)002:644: dbyings ka dag /ngo bo snang stong gnyis med la
NK083('u)002:645: tha dad kyi gnyis chos ka nas dag pa ni
NK083('u)002:647: gnyis pa lhun grub la gsum ste /
NK083('u)002:648: sems kyi rtsal snang sna tshogs su 'char ba la gzhan nas btsal mi dgos te /
NK083('u)002:651: shar tshad kyi rang bzhin stong pa las gzhan nas btsal mi dgos te /
NK083('u)002:652: shar ba po rang stong pa ni /
NK083('u)002:654: ngo bo snang stong gnyis med la btsal mi dgos te /
NK083('u)002:655: gang snang de dag rang gnyis su med pa ni /
NK083('u)002:657: gsum pa kun gyi bdag nyid du gnas pa ni /
NK083('u)002:658: chos thams cad ni rang gi sems yin la /
NK083('u)002:659: sems kyi rnam pa cir yang ma 'gags pa /
NK083('u)002:661: ngo bo cir yang mi rtog pa /
NK083('u)002:662: de chos thams cad kyi bdag nyid do //
NK083('u)002:663: de ka gzhi snang stong gnyis med kyi bdag nyid du bstan te /
NK083('u)002:664: rnam pa cir yang ma 'gags pa /
NK083('u)002:665: gzhi snang ba gshis cir yang ma grub pa /
NK083('u)002:666: gzhi stong pa ngo bo cir yang mi rtog pa /
NK083('u)002:667: gzhi gnyis med kyi bdag nyid do //
NK083('u)002:668: de ka lta ba bskyed rdzogs gnyis kyi bdag nyid kyang yin te /
NK083('u)002:671: mi rtog pa gnyis med do //
NK083('u)002:672: bsgom pa zhi gnas lhag mthong gi bdag nyid kyang yin te /
NK083('u)002:675: mi rtog pa gnyis med do //
NK083('u)002:676: 'bras bu sangs rgyas sku gsum gyi bdag nyid kyang yin te /
NK083('u)002:680: mkhyen pa gnyis ldan gyi ye shes kyang yin te /
NK083('u)002:682: ma grub pa ci lta ba /
NK083('u)002:683: mi rtog pa gnyis med du mkhyen pa'o //
NK083('u)002:684: spangs rtogs phun sum tshogs pa yang yin te /
NK083('u)002:686: ma grub pa spangs pa phun sum tshogs pa'o //
NK083('u)002:687: de ltar shes pas 'khor 'das skyon yon lha 'dre
NK083('u)002:688: la sogs pa mnyam pa nyid du la bzla ba
NK083('u)002:689: yin te / snang ba ma 'gags pa rang snang du mnyam /
NK083('u)002:690: ma grub pa stong par mnyam /
NK083('u)002:691: ngo bo mi rtog par gnyis med du mnyam mo //
NK083('u)002:692: de tsam na snang tshad gzhi dngos po'i gnas lugs /
NK083('u)002:693: lta ba bskyed rdzogs kyi yo langs /
NK083('u)002:694: sgom pa zhi gnas lhag mthong gi rang bzhin /
NK083('u)002:695: 'bras bu sangs rgyas sku gsum gyi dkyil 'khor las mi 'da' ste /
NK083('u)002:696: rang snang rang ngo shes nas gzhan snang gi rtog pa med /
NK083('u)002:697: rang stong rang ngo shes nas dngos po rang rgyud pa'i bden 'dzin bral /
NK083('u)002:698: gnyis med rang ngo shes na tha dad gnyis 'dzin med /
NK083('u)002:699: de tsam na stong pa rgyu 'bras su 'char ba thams cad mkhyen pa'i khyad chos /
NK083('u)002:700: rgyu 'bras stong par rtogs pas mnyam pa nyid chen por la bazla'o //
NK083('u)002:701: chos thams cad snang tsam du yod pa kun rdzob bden pa'i pho sgo /
NK083('u)002:702: bden med dngos su grub pa med pa don dam bden pa'i rang gzhung /
NK083('u)002:703: chos thams cad yod pa yang ma yin /
NK083('u)002:707: skyon ye dag /yon tan ye rdzogs /
NK083('u)002:709: gnyis ma grub pa'i gnyis med /
NK083('u)002:710: zung ma rnyed pa'i zung 'jug /mtha' ma rnyed pa'i mtha' bral /
NK083('u)002:711: bzang ngan ma rnyed pa'i kun tu bzang po /
NK083('u)002:712: btsal mi dgos pa'i lhun grub /
NK083('u)002:713: 'khrul pa med pa'i ka dag go //
NK083('u)002:714: bar lag thams cad rmings nas 'gyed la /
NK083('u)002:715: 'gram rdo thams cad rtsad nas thon /
NK083('u)002:716: tham thum thams cad gcig tu 'dres /
NK083('u)002:717: 'khor 'das kyi chos thams cad gdod nas rnam par grol ba min pa gcig kyang med do //
NK083('u)002:718: sems nyid gcer ston gyi lag khrid lnga pa /
NK083('u)002:719: gsang sngags lam gyi rim pa rin po che gsal ba'i sgron me'i khrid chung +thii /
NK083('u)002:720: gsang sngags lam gyi rim pa'i don khrid ngo sprod
NK083('u)002:721: du gdab pa rgad po 'khar tshugs dang rgan mo
NK083('u)002:722: mdzub tshugs kyi gdams ngag bzhugs so //
NK083('u)002:725: rngog shes rab rgyal po zhes bya ba /
NK083('u)002:728: dad pa dang ldan pa gcig gis /
NK083('u)002:729: brag po che'i dben rtsa ru /
NK083('u)002:730: slob dpon lo gcig bzhugs de /
NK083('u)002:731: rngog gis kyang chos zhu ma byas /
NK083('u)002:732: slob dpon gyis kyang chos bshad ma byas par /
NK083('u)002:733: lo gcig na slob dpon bzhud par dgongs pa la /
NK083('u)002:734: rngog gis gser srang gang gis man+dala gyi me tog byas nas slob dpon la phul te /
NK083('u)002:736: slob dpon rin po che lags /
NK083('u)002:737: bdag la thugs brtse bar dgongs 'tshal /
NK083('u)002:738: bdag gcig tu thos pa chung /
NK083('u)002:747: rgad po 'chi kha ma'i gdams ngag cig zhu 'tshal /
NK083('u)002:750: rgad po'i snying gar phyag 'khar btsugs te gdams pa ni 'adi'o //
NK083('u)002:751: nyon cig /rang rig pa byang chub kyi sems 'di la ltos dang /
NK083('u)002:752: gzugs dang kha dog tu grub pa med /
NK083('u)002:753: phyogs dang ris su chad pa med /
NK083('u)002:754: mtha' dang dbus su grub pa med /
NK083('u)002:755: dang po byung sa med de stong /
NK083('u)002:756: bar du gnas sa med de stong /
NK083('u)002:757: tha ma 'gro sa med de stong /
NK083('u)002:758: stong pa de ga ngo shes na /
NK083('u)002:759: rang ngo rang gis shes pa yin /
NK083('u)002:760: chos kyi chos nyid go ba yin /
NK083('u)002:761: sems kyis sems mthong ba yin /
NK083('u)002:762: dngos po'i gnas lugs gtan la phebs pa yin /
NK083('u)002:763: rig pa byang chub kyi sems de dngos po cir yang ma grub cing /
NK083('u)002:764: rang byung rang la gnas pas /
NK083('u)002:765: gzhan nas btsal du med de /
NK083('u)002:766: chos nyid don rtogs par sla /
NK083('u)002:767: chos nyid kyi don la re dogs kyi 'dzin pa med de /
NK083('u)002:768: sems rtag chad kyi mtha' las 'das /
NK083('u)002:769: sangs la rgya rgyu med de /
NK083('u)002:773: sangs rgyas la re ba med de /
NK083('u)002:775: dmyal bar dogs pa med de /
NK083('u)002:776: rig pa rang dag /chos la bya rgyu med de /
NK083('u)002:777: rig pa chos nyid rang gsal /
NK083('u)002:778: lta ba gnas lugs chen po rang la yod pas /
NK083('u)002:779: gzhan la btsal rgyu med par thag bcad do //
NK083('u)002:780: de ltar rtogs nas nyams su len par 'dod na /
NK083('u)002:781: rang gang na 'dug pa de lus ri bo'i dgon gnas yin pas /
NK083('u)002:782: phyi snang ba la gang snang ba de rang snang /
NK083('u)002:786: spros pa'i mtha' thams cad dang bral bar bzhag go //
NK083('u)002:787: de nas phyi'i snang ba grogs su shar bas snang
NK083('u)002:788: ba rang sar dag /snang ba rang sar dag pas
NK083('u)002:789: snang ba lam du khyer nas nyams su blang bade'o
NK083('u)002:790: // nang sems la dran pa ci shar 'gyus kyang /
NK083('u)002:791: de'i ngang la ngo bo med de stong bar 'dug
NK083('u)002:792: pas 'gyu dran rang sar dag /sems la gsal thebs
NK083('u)002:793: lam du slong ba nyams su blang bade'o //
NK083('u)002:794: gsang ba nyon mongs pa gang skyes kyang nyon mongs pa la bltas na rjes med de /
NK083('u)002:795: rang byung rang zhi nyon mongs pa lam du khyer nas nyams su blang ba de'o //
NK083('u)002:796: de ltar nyams su lon tsa na sgom pa la thun bsgom byar med /
NK083('u)002:797: thams cad grogs su shar bas nyams la gsal 'grib med de //
NK083('u)002:798: chos nyid kyi ye shes la rgyun chad med /
NK083('u)002:799: spyod lam la spang blang med /
NK083('u)002:800: ji ltar 'dug kyang chos nyid kyi don dang 'du 'bral med do //
NK083('u)002:802: 'byung ba'i lus rgas kyang byang chub kyi sems la rgas rgyu med /
NK083('u)002:803: dbang po rno brtul med do //
NK083('u)002:804: rnam rig gi rten lus zhig kyang /
NK083('u)002:805: rig pa ye shes chos kyi sku la rgyun chad med pas mi 'gyur zhing brtan pa thob pas /
NK083('u)002:806: tshe la ring thung med do //
NK083('u)002:807: chos nyid kyi don la phyogs ris med pas /
NK083('u)002:808: don go bas thos pa la che chung med do //
NK083('u)002:809: rgad po yang dag pa'i lam de'i don nyams su longs mdzod cig /nyams len rgyud la 'khol mdzod /
NK083('u)002:810: tshig dang don du ma bral bar mdzod /
NK083('u)002:811: brtson 'grus kyi grogs dang ma bral bar mdzod /
NK083('u)002:812: dran pa'i rtsis zin par mdzod /
NK083('u)002:813: long gtam dang 'chal gtam la ma dga' bar mdzod /
NK083('u)002:814: tha mal gyi blo dang bral bar mdzod /
NK083('u)002:815: bu tsha bo la zhen pa ma che bar mdzod /
NK083('u)002:816: bza' btung la sred pa ma che bar mdzod /
NK083('u)002:817: tha mal pa shi ba la soms mdzod /
NK083('u)002:818: tshe la long med brtson 'grus bskyed mdzod /
NK083('u)002:819: rgas po 'chi kha ma'i gdams ngag mdzod cig /gsungs
NK083('u)002:820: nas rgad po'i snying khar phyag 'khar btsugs nas gdams
NK083('u)002:821: pas / rngog shes rab rgyal po grub pa thob bo //
NK083('u)002:822: rgad po 'khar btsug gi gdams pa sangs rgyas ngo sprod ces bya ba /
NK083('u)002:823: phyi rabs kyi don du mkhar chen bza' mtsho rgyal gyis yi ger bkod pa'o //
NK083('u)002:826: slob dpon pad+ma 'byung gnas rgyal po khri srong lde'u btsan gyis spyan drangs nas /
NK083('u)002:827: brag dmar bsam yas na bzhugs pa'i dus su /
NK083('u)002:828: dad ldan bza' dge ldan ma zhes bya ba /
NK083('u)002:829: rgan mo dad pa che ba /
NK083('u)002:830: slob dpon la shin tu mos pa gcig yod pa des /
NK083('u)002:831: g.yog mo mar gong bza' rin chen mtsho zhes bya ba la /
NK083('u)002:832: nang bar chab zho zhal bu re la rgun 'brum gyi bye tshum re btab nas /
NK083('u)002:833: slob dpon la drang du btang ngo //
NK083('u)002:834: de nas slob dpon bsam yas su bzhud pa'i lam
NK083('u)002:835: khar rgan mos phyag dang bskor ba byas nas zhus
NK083('u)002:836: pa / slob dpon chen po lags /
NK083('u)002:837: slob dpon ni bzhud kha ma /
NK083('u)002:839: bdag gcig tu bud med kyi lus thob pas skye ba dman /
NK083('u)002:840: gnyis su blo dman pas shes rab dang thos pa chung /
NK083('u)002:841: gsum du na so rgas shes pa rmugs nas mig mi gsal bas /
NK083('u)002:842: slob dpon chen pos rgan mo la /
NK083('u)002:843: tshegs chung ba go sla ba /
NK083('u)002:844: nyams su blang bde ba don che ba /
NK083('u)002:845: rgan mo 'chi kha ma'i gdams ngag gcig zhu 'tshal /
NK083('u)002:848: rgan mo khyod su yin gsungs pas /
NK083('u)002:852: chab zho zhal bu re 'dren du btang ba de lags /
NK083('u)002:855: khri srong lde'u btsan pas kyang dad pa che ba gcig de yin ang gsungs nas /
NK083('u)002:856: rgan mo dpon g.yog la gdams pa btab pa /
NK083('u)002:857: rgan mo skyil krung bcas la /
NK083('u)002:859: dar cig sems klod la zhog cig /gsungs nas /
NK083('u)002:860: slob dpon gyis rgan mo'i snying gar mdzub mo btsugs te gdams pa btab pa ni 'adi'o //
NK083('u)002:861: rgan mo nyon mdzod cig /yang dag par rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas kyi dgongs pa dang /
NK083('u)002:862: khams gsum gyi sems can gnyis la khyad par ci yod byas na /
NK083('u)002:863: sems rtogs ma rtogs gnyis las med /
NK083('u)002:864: sems nyid kyi don rtogs pas sangs rgyas /
NK083('u)002:865: ma rtogs pas 'khor bar 'khyams pa yin /
NK083('u)002:866: sangs rgyas kyi ye shes rang la yod kyang ngo ma shes pa yin /
NK083('u)002:867: de yang sangs rgyas kyi rgyu de sems can thams cad la yod /
NK083('u)002:868: sgos dal 'byor thob pa'i mi la yod de /
NK083('u)002:869: de yang skyes pa la sangs rgyas kyi rgyu che la /
NK083('u)002:870: bud med la sangs rgyas kyi rgyu chung ba med /
NK083('u)002:871: des na skye ba bud med du skyes kyang 'gal ba med do gsungs /
NK083('u)002:872: de la ye shes de rtogs shing shes par byed pa la /
NK083('u)002:873: sangs rgyas kyis chos kyi sgo mo brgyad khri bzhi stong gsungs kyang /
NK083('u)002:874: de'i don shes par byed pa la /
NK083('u)002:875: bla ma'i gdams ngag gi tshig gsum du 'dus pas /
NK083('u)002:876: blo dman zhing shes rab chung yang mi lto gsungs /
NK083('u)002:877: de ltar chos nyid kyi don sangs rgyas kyi dgongs pa tshig gsum ni /
NK083('u)002:878: phyi gzung ba'i yul dag pas snang ba rang sar grol /
NK083('u)002:879: nang 'dzin ba'i sems dag pas 'dzin med kyi rig pa rang sar grol /
NK083('u)002:880: bar du 'od gsal nyams dga' nas rang ngo rang gis shes pa'o //
NK083('u)002:881: de la phyi gzung ba'i yul ji ltar dag na /
NK083('u)002:882: rig pa byang chub kyi sems 'di la /
NK083('u)002:883: rnam rtog gi blos ma bslad par rang gsal du snang ba 'di la bzhag pas /
NK083('u)002:884: yul snang ba la 'dzin pa ma zhugs pas /
NK083('u)002:885: snang ba gang ltar yang don du bden par mi 'dzin te /
NK083('u)002:887: sa rdo ri brag /rtsi shing nags tshal /
NK083('u)002:892: bu dang khyo la sogs pa gang la'ang bdag tu 'dzin pa ma zhugs /
NK083('u)002:893: snang yang don du mi 'dzin cing zhen pa med pa de /
NK083('u)002:894: phyi gzung ba'i yul dag pa bya ba yin /
NK083('u)002:895: gzung ba'i yul dag pa zer na'ang rang bzhin med mi 'gro /
NK083('u)002:896: zhen pa dang 'dzin pa med pa /
NK083('u)002:898: dper na me long nang gi gzugs brnyan ltar /
NK083('u)002:899: snang yang gzung rgyu dang 'dzin pa med de /
NK083('u)002:900: stong pa 'dra bas snang yang rang sar stong ba'o //
NK083('u)002:901: nang 'dzin pa'i sems dag pas rig pa rang sar grol ba'i man ngag ni /
NK083('u)002:902: sems rnam rtog 'gyu byed kyi dran pa dang /
NK083('u)002:904: gang dran pa de la blos ma bzung bas /
NK083('u)002:905: 'gyu ba rang sangs su 'gro bas stong ste /
NK083('u)002:906: 'gyu byed kyi skyon gyis ma gos pa'o //
NK083('u)002:907: nang rig pa dri ma med pa zer nas /
NK083('u)002:908: bem po sa rdo ltar 'gro ba med /
NK083('u)002:909: rig pa la rtog pa'i dri mas ma 'dzin pa la zer ba yin /
NK083('u)002:910: dper na rin po che gser gling du phyin pa 'dra /
NK083('u)002:911: gser gyi gling du phyin tsam na /
NK083('u)002:912: sa rdo'i ming yang med pa bzhin du /
NK083('u)002:913: rang rig pa'i ye shes su grol tsam na /
NK083('u)002:914: rnam rtog gi ming yang med pa yin /
NK083('u)002:916: bar du 'od gsal nyams dga' ba'i man ngag ni /
NK083('u)002:917: de nyams su blangs pa'i dus su /
NK083('u)002:918: rang rig pa dri ma med pa la sa le
NK083('u)002:919: sang nge hrig ge ba de nyams su blangs pas
NK083('u)002:920: / bde ba gsal ba mi rtog pa gsum /
NK083('u)002:921: zhen 'dzin dang blo yis ma bslad pa'i nyams gcig 'ong bas /
NK083('u)002:922: de sangs rgyas kyi dgongs pa yin pas rang ngo rang gis shes pa'o //
NK083('u)002:923: dper na rang gi yin pa la 'di nga'i yin ched du bsgom mi dgos /
NK083('u)002:924: ma yin snyam pa'i rnam par rtog pa gang yang mi 'char ro //
NK083('u)002:925: dpe de dang 'dra bar rang gis rang rig pa
NK083('u)002:926: rang chos nyid yin par rang gis ngo shes tsam
NK083('u)002:927: na / 'khor ba'i chos thams cad chos nyid stong pa nyid yin snyam du bsgom du mi dgos /
NK083('u)002:928: ma bsgoms kyang chos nyid kyi don dang mi 'bral te /
NK083('u)002:929: ma bsgoms pa'i bsgom pa bya ba yin no //
NK083('u)002:931: chos thams cad rang bzhin med par shes pa de /
NK083('u)002:933: rig pa chos kyi dbyings ngo shes pas rang ngo rang gis shes pa bya ba yin no //
NK083('u)002:935: skye ba la mtho dman med /
NK083('u)002:936: bya ba la che chung med /
NK083('u)002:938: shes rab la che chung med /
NK083('u)002:939: thos pa la mang nyung med /
NK083('u)002:940: na so la rgas gzhon med /
NK083('u)002:941: shes pa la gsal mi gsal med /
NK083('u)002:942: tshegs chung la go sla ba /
NK083('u)002:943: nyams len bde la don che ba /
NK083('u)002:944: 'chi ba la nyams mi nga ba /
NK083('u)002:946: de ltar nyams su len mdzod /
NK083('u)002:947: tshe la long med pas rtsol ba bskyed mdzad /
NK083('u)002:948: bu khyo'i khol bor glags med lo stong byed pa las /
NK083('u)002:949: rig pa skad cig bsgoms pas bskyed che /
NK083('u)002:950: bla mas gdams pa'i brgyag myur du thon /
NK083('u)002:951: tshe 'di'i bya ba la zin dus med pas sgom sgrub mthar byung mdzod /
NK083('u)002:952: rgan mo 'chi kha mi 'tsher ba'i sun mar gdams pa 'di thong mdzod /
NK083('u)002:954: rgan mo'i snying gar phyag mdzub btsugs nas gdams pa btab pas /
NK083('u)002:955: ming yang rgan mo mdzub btsug gi gdams pa zhes bya'o //
NK083('u)002:956: rgan mo dpon g.yog gnyis grol te grub pa thob bo //
NK083('u)002:957: phyi rabs kyi don du mkhar chen bza' mtsho rgyal gyi yi ger bkod pa'o //
NK083('u)002:958: rgan mo mdzub btsug gi gdams ngag rdzogs so //
NK083('u)002:959: de ltar gsang sngags phyi nang gi lam rim rtsa
NK083('u)002:960: ba dang bsdus don rang 'grel gsang ba'i man ngag
NK083('u)002:961: ngo sprod rnam pa gsum dang bcas pa 'di dag
NK083('u)002:962: slob dpon chen po pad+ma sam b+ha ba'i gsang bka'
NK083('u)002:964: lo ts+aa ba chen po gnyags dz+ny+aa na ku m+aa ra dang /
NK083('u)002:965: gnubs sangs rgyas ye shes nas rim par bka' ma'i brgyud pa bar ma chad par bzhugs pa'o //
NK083('u)002:966: bar mtshams su lo rgyus kyi che ba dang mtshams
NK083('u)002:967: sbyor gyi tshig rnams lo ts+aa ba'i gsung yin par
NK083('u)002:968: snang ngo // phyis su nyang gur gyi gter kha gong 'og gnyis dang /
NK083('u)002:969: gter chen rdo rje gling pa bcas kyi gter byon
NK083('u)002:970: rnams dang tshig don 'dra bar bzhugs pas yid ches
NK083('u)002:971: pa'i gnas su bzung bar 'os pa'o //
NK083('u)002:972: khyab bdag bla ma mtsho skyes rdo rje yis //
NK083('u)002:973: tshe rabs kun tu 'bral med rjes bzung ste //
NK083('u)002:974: rdzogs smin sbyangs gsum sa lam myur bgrod nas //
NK083('u)002:975: zung 'jug sku bzhi'i 'bras bu mngon gyur shog /khyad
NK083('u)002:976: par dmu god snyigs ma'i 'gro /gsang chen theg rtse'i
NK083('u)002:977: gdul skal du // rgyal bas basngagasa pa'i lam mchog 'di //
NK083('u)002:978: yun gnas phan bde'i dpal gyur cig /ces pa'ang rnying
NK083('u)002:979: bstan btsas su gu ru pad+ma'i gsung skor dpe bskrun
NK083('u)002:980: bgyi skabs ka m+aa la'i ming gis smon pa'o //
